text.tspan: ENTER GEOMETRY DATA IN THE FOLLOWING FORM:
ref. ID bias ID thickness per region origin coordinates nreg
EXTENDED GEOMETRY REGION INPUT DATA REQUIREMENTS
Enter the X Y Z coordinates of the most negative point
Enter the X Y Z coordinates of the origin
number of regions to be generated
The number of dimensions to be entered is the same as the region preceding the replicate or reflector specification because the g
enerated regions have that shape. The value of the dimensions is the
thickness of each generated region of material on that surfac
e and must therefore be a positive value.
